heading: World politics. Caricatures and cartoons.
general-note: Here are entered works consisting of general collections of political cartoons. Works consisting of collections of political cartoons pertaining to a specific region, country, city, etc., are entered under the name of the place with subdivision. History--Caricatures and cartoons. or. Politics and government--Caricatures and cartoons.. Works on the history and art of drawing political cartoons are entered under. Political cartoons..
